{"article_id":"F2r8fyumxEFF7Bfj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"North Korea 's decision","depth":11},{"id":1,"text":"to meet US President Donald Trump","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"proves","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"the US strategy","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"of isolating North Korea","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"is working ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"US Vice-President Mike Pence says .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"The US has made `` zero concessions '' ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"and would maintain pressure","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"until denuclearisation was achieved .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"But the White House later said","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"North Korea would have to take `` concrete steps '' before any meeting .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Only months ago , Mr Trump and North Korean leader Kim Jong-un were hurling insults at each other .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"But now Mr Trump has agreed to the summit","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"following an invitation","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"delivered by South Korea .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"No sitting US president has ever met a North Korean leader .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"President Trump tweeted","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"that a `` deal with North Korea is very much in the making '' .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Skip Twitter post by @ realDonaldTrump","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"The deal with North Korea is very much in the making","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"and will be ,","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"if completed ,","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"a very good one for the World .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"Time and place to be determined .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"March 10 , 2018 Report","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Earlier he has hailed the move as `` great progress '' ,","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"but he said","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"sanctions would remain in place","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"until a denuclearisation deal was reached .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"The North has halted missile and nuclear tests during previous talks ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"only to resume them","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"when it lost patience","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"or felt","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"it was not getting","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"what it demanded ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"analysts say .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Some expressed concern","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"the Trump regime could `` fall into the North Korean trap ''","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"of granting concessions with nothing tangible in return .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Later , White House spokesperson Sarah Sanders said","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"the president would demand `` concrete steps and concrete actions ''","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"from North Korea","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"before any meeting took place .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"She did not specify","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"what those steps were ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"nor repeat previous assertions","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"that the meeting would take place by May .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"There has been no mention of the developments as yet on North Korean state media .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"In Sweden , meanwhile , local diplomatic sources were quoted as saying","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"the North 's Foreign Minister Ri Yong-ho would be visiting his Swedish counterpart soon .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"The Swedish embassy in Pyongyang represents US , Canadian and Australian diplomatic interests there .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"South Korean President Moon Jae-in has acknowledged","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"there are obstacles ahead .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"He is managing expectations","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"and so much can go wrong .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"His approval ratings took a hit during the Winter Olympics","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"after he integrated the women 's hockey team with players from the North","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"and met a general from Pyongyang","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"who had been accused of masterminding deadly attacks on South Koreans ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"though they have since rebounded .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"These talks are a huge gamble with a communist state","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"which is hard to read .","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"But","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"if , just if , he helps pull it off ,","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"it may reduce the threat of nuclear war","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"and he could win himself a Nobel Peace Prize .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"The South Korean envoys met Mr Kim in Pyongyang this week .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"It was the culmination of a rapprochement","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"that began at the New Year","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"and saw the Koreas marching together at the Winter Olympics .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"The envoys then travelled to Washington","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"to brief Mr Trump .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Speaking outside the White House after the meeting ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"South Korean National Security Adviser Chung Eui-yong said","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"Mr Kim was prepared to sit down with the US president","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"and was now `` committed to denuclearisation '' .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"In a statement","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"sent to the Washington Post ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"North Korea 's UN ambassador said","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"the `` courageous decision '' of Mr Kim would help secure `` peace and stability in the Korean peninsula and the East Asia region '' .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"There is no indication yet","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"of where the Trump-Kim talks might take place ,","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"but the Korean border 's demilitarised zone","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"( DMZ )","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"and Beijing are seen as likely options .","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"Clearly for the US , South Korea and allied nations , denuclearisation is the key issue .","depth":3},{"id":90,"text":"North Korea has been isolated for decades","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"because of its pursuit of nuclear weapons , in defiance of international laws .","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"The North has carried out six nuclear tests","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"and has missiles","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"that could reach the US .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"However , the BBC 's Laura Bicker in Seoul says","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"it is important to note that North Korea has not yet promised to abandon its nuclear weapons completely .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"The North 's well-documented human rights abuses are also a key issue for the US .","depth":5},{"id":98,"text":"So what does the North want ?","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"An easing , if not removal , of sanctions certainly .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"Perhaps a peace treaty","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"to finally end the Korean War","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"and a promise","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"if North Korea denuclearised","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"then the US would finally withdraw its troops from South Korea .","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"The US has tens of thousands of military personnel there","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"and the massive annual joint war games infuriate the North","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"because it believes","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"they are preparation for invasion .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"The UN was among the most positive ,","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"with Secretary-General Antonio Guterres commending the `` leadership and vision '' of all concerned .","depth":5},{"id":112,"text":"Chinese President Xi Jinping telephoned Donald Trump on Friday","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"to welcome the development","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"and urge all sides to avoid doing anything","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"that could impede the improving situation .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"Russia , Germany , the EU and the IAEA all voiced hope","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"that talks would reduce the risk","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"of conflict erupting .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"Other countries , such as Japan and the UK , vowed to keep up the pressure on the North to give up its nuclear ambitions .","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"In the US , reaction was divided","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"- not least in Mr Trump 's own party .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"`` The North Korean racket for decades now has been to offer talks in exchange for bribes or other advantages .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"Then we pay them ,","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"and make an agreement ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"when they cheat","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"it all breaks down","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"- until the next time , ''","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"Elliott Abrams , foreign policy adviser to Ronald Reagan and George W Bush , told CBS News ,","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"`` I hope","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"we are not about to fall into their trap yet again . ''","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"But Senator Lindsey Graham told the same news outlet","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"although he was `` not naive '' ,","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"President Trump 's `` strong stand against North Korea and its nuclear aggression gives us the best hope in decades","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"to resolve this threat peacefully '' .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":273,"left":206,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":191,"right":205,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left"